de.tudresden.inf.rn.mobilis.sea.jingle.connection.manager.observer

Class SessionObserver

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.tudresden.inf.rn.mobilis.sea.jingle.connection.manager.observer.SessionObserver

  • public class SessionObserver
extends java.lang.Object
    This auxiliary SessionObserver is used to lazy add ReceptionListeners and Raw media types when a JingleSession has been created (so you may add the prototypes and listeners at any time)
